investigation.title: miRNA signature detection and countermeasures against HZE radiation exposure for tissue degeneration-Heart tissue
investigation.description: Biological risks associated with space radiation and microgravity are major concerns for long-term space travel. Through a Systems Biology approach, our previous NASA work has shown both TGFÎ² signaling pathways and miRNAs have a critical impact on defining health risks with and without space irradiation.
